## Additional Terms for Production Use

While this software is provided under the MIT License, users deploying this 
template in production environments are strongly advised to:

1. Implement additional security measures appropriate for their use case
2. Ensure compliance with applicable data protection laws (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
3. Obtain proper user consent for data collection and processing
4. Follow YouTube API Terms of Service and rate limits
5. Implement appropriate access controls and authentication
6. Regular security audits and monitoring

The authors disclaim any responsibility for misuse of this template or 
failure to implement appropriate security measures. 